Pre-Game Insights: Dejounte Murray and Zion Williamson will play together for the first time this season.
Murray highlighted CJ McCollum's recent strong performance and expressed his admiration for the player.
Others: Zion Williamson has been sidelined since Nov. 6 due to a left hamstring strain.
Murray was out for more than a month after breaking his left hand during the Oct. 23 season opener vs. Chicago.
